{"pin":"BH02628","subcodes":[{"code":"BH02628","anchor":"","first_line":"Grieve thou not in thine exile. By God! Wert thou to behold through Mine eyes, thou wouldst sacrifice thyself in My path, through that which God hath made thee to be [3.5s]... ...Call thou to mind the behavior of Ashraf’s mother, whose son laid down his life in the Land of Zá (Zanján). He, most certainly, is in the seat of truth","first_line_orig":"لا تجزعی من غربتک تالله لو تنظرین بعینی لتفدین نفسک فی سبیلی بما جعلک الله  ","language":"1","word_count":"340","subjects":"@steadfastness; perseverance; faithfulness, @the Kingdom of God [Malakut], @spiritual emotions and susceptibilities, @consolation and comfort","notes":" \u003ca href=\"http://web.archive.org/web/20070930181707/http://bahai-library.com/resources/leiden.list/leiden.list.html#363\"\u003eLL#363\u003c/a\u003e","translations":[],"writing_refs":[{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"sq","lang_name":"Albanian"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"te","lang_name":"Telugu"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"es","lang_name":"Spanish"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"it","lang_name":"Italian"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"ja","lang_name":"Japanese"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"ko","lang_name":"Korean"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"el","lang_name":"Greek"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"fr","lang_name":"French"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"pl","lang_name":"Polish"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"sk","lang_name":"Slovak"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"sv","lang_name":"Swedish"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"ta","lang_name":"Tamil"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"tvl","lang_name":"Tuvalu"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleani